			<description><![CDATA[<div class="feed-description"><p><span class="userContent">
<table>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>
<p><span class="userContent">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img alt="RADDEL Workshop a" src="https://projects.icmab.es/raddel/images/RADDEL%20Workshop%20a.jpg" height="502" width="350" />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span><br /><br /></p>
</td>
<td>
<p><span class="userContent"><span class="userContent"><span class="userContent"><span class="userContent"><img alt="RADDEL Workshop b" src="https://projects.icmab.es/raddel/images/RADDEL%20Workshop%20b.jpg" height="495" width="350" /></span></span></span></span></p>
