</span></p>
<p><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><span style="color: #000000;"><span class="userContent">Next 10th of October, the First RADDEL Workshop on Complimentary Training will take place at the Conference Room of the Institute of Materials Science of Barcelona (ICMAB-CSIC).</span>The workshop, titled "R&amp;D Project Management and Technology Transfer: from Research to the Market", is part of the training activities of the european project RADDEL</span> <span style="color: #000000;">(</span><a href="http://www.icmab.es/raddel/">http://www.icmab.es/raddel/</a><span style="color: #000000;">), an Initial Training Network (ITN) funded by the European Comission under the FP7 (Marie-Curie Actions).</span></span></p>
